title: Amy's Daughter Celebrates Her First Birthday In The States + Will It Uber: A Winning Lottery Ticket + Morgan #2 Gives An Update On Her Dinner With Bobby
itunes:title: Amy's Daughter Celebrates Her First Birthday In The States + Will It Uber: A Winning Lottery Ticket + Morgan #2 Gives An Update On Her Dinner With Bobby
description:
Amy's daughter just celebrated her 11th birthday, and Amy threw a big party for her over the weekend. Amy recaps the highlights this morning. The show attempts a round of "Will It Uber" with a winning lottery ticket. Also, Morgan #2 tells us about her dinner with Bobby.
